### 结果API测试

### 变量设置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081/api
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 用户登录获取Token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 获取所有结果
GET {{baseUrl}}/results
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 获取单个结果
GET {{baseUrl}}/results/d7e6f8c9-142d-4b5a-9e3f-1a2b3c4d5e6f
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 创建新结果
POST {{baseUrl}}/results
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "测试结果标题",
  "description": "这是一个用于测试的结果描述，包含详细的结果内容。",
  "relatedRequirementId": "b8f4c5a2-035c-480d-9e7a-e8fcdeba965b"
}

### 更新结果
PUT {{baseUrl}}/results/d7e6f8c9-142d-4b5a-9e3f-1a2b3c4d5e6f
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "更新后的结果标题",
  "description": "这是更新后的结果描述内容。",
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

### 删除结果
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/results/d7e6f8c9-142d-4b5a-9e3f-1a2b3c4d5e6f
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 获取与特定需求相关的结果
GET {{baseUrl}}/results/by-requirement/b8f4c5a2-035c-480d-9e7a-e8fcdeba965b
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}